result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="800"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  okText="提交意见"
  @ok="handleOk"
  @cancel="handleCancel"
  cancelText="关闭">

  <a-select v-model="selectedModel" style="width: 260px;margin-bottom:20px;" @change="selectval"  v-decorator="[ 'ibusModelId', {}]">
    <!--<a-select-option v-for="(item,index) in modelData" :key="index" :value="item.iid">{{item.sname}}</a-select-option>-->
    <a-select-option value="你好">你好</a-select-option>
    <a-select-option value="我好">我好</a-select-option>
    <a-select-option value="大家好">大家好</a-select-option>
    <a-select-option value="世界好">世界好</a-select-option>
  </a-select>
  <a-textarea :rows="6" placeholder="请填选意见" v-model="areatext"></a-textarea>
</a-modal>
